graph TD
    A[Put on PPE: lab coat, goggles, gloves] --> B[Clean work area with 70% ethanol]
    B --> C[Light Bunsen burner]
    C --> D[Gather sterile materials]
    D --> E[Flame sterilize inoculating loop]
    E --> F{Using culture tube?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Remove tube cap without setting it down]
    F -->|No| H[Open culture plate near flame]
    G --> I[Flame tube mouth]
    H --> J[Transfer sample using sterile technique]
    I --> J
    J --> K{Using culture tube?}
    K -->|Yes| L[Re-flame tube mouth]
    K -->|No| M[Close culture plate]
    L --> N[Replace tube cap]
    M --> O[Flame sterilize loop again]
    N --> O
    O --> P{More transfers needed?}
    P -->|Yes| E
    P -->|No| Q[Turn off Bunsen burner]
    Q --> R[Dispose of materials in biohazard container]
    R --> S[Clean work area again]
    S --> T[Remove PPE: gloves, coat, goggles]
    T --> U[Wash hands thoroughly]
    U --> V[Record in lab notebook]
